arts.ttl: Liverpool fail to beat Ole Gunnar Solskjaer's Premier League record after Fulham loss
arts.sum: Liverpool lost 3-2 at Fulham on Sunday and while the Reds remain 11 points clear of Arsenal in the Premier League title race, their chances of eclipsing a record held by Manchester United have been dashed

arts.ttl: Preview: Kasimpasa vs. Besiktas - prediction, team news, lineups
arts.sum: Sports Mole previews Monday's Turkish Super Lig clash between Kasimpasa and Besiktas, including predictions, team news and possible lineups.
